{
  "id": "shader",
  "title": "C#与Shader交互：使用脚本控制shader属性",
  "date": "2026-06-08",
  "summary": "使用C#脚本来控制Shader中的属性的一些注意事项。",
  "tags": [
    "UnityEngine",
    "shader",
    "C#"
  ],
  "content": [
    "# 概述",
    "",
    "通过脚本来驱动使用同一个shader的多个材质属性值。",
    "",
    "",
    "# 内容",
    "",
    "",
    "## 全局修改",
    "",
    "1. ShaderGraph",
    "",
    "<img class=\"blog-img blog-img-align-center\" src=\"assets/ImageWork/Blog/Shader/shader属性控制-01.png\" alt=\"图片\">",
    "",
    "声明一个属性之后，需要将该属性按红框内设置.",
    "",
    "对于shaderGraph，全局属性不能公开在外部，否则无法生效（如果勾选，则Global将失效）。",
    "",
    "勾选Property重写选项。",
    "",
    "设置属性为Global类型。",
    "",
    "",
    "",
    "",
    "1. code",
    "",
    "",
    "```cpp",
    "Properties",
    "{",
    "    //_Clip(\"Clip\" , float) = 0.5",
    "}",
    "",
    "CBUFFER_START(UnityPerMaterial) ",
    "CBUFFER_END",
    "float4 _Clip;    //GlobalProperty属性不能放在CBUFFER里面，会破坏SRPBatch机制",
    "```",
    "",
    "",
    "",
    "",
    "如果是代码，则该属性 不能 在Properites中声明让其公开在属性面板，否则将无法生效，应该直接在CBUFFER_STATR之外定义。如果定义在了CBUFFER_STATR中，将会破坏SRP Batch机制。",
    "",
    "",
    "",
    "",
    "1. C#脚本",
    "",
    "",
    "```cpp",
    "public class GlobalProperty : MonoBehaviour",
    "{",
    "    [Range(0.0f, 1.0f)] ",
    "    public float clipValue = 0.0f;",
    "",
    "    void Update()",
    "    {",
    "        Shader.SetGlobalFloat(\"_Clip\" , clipValue);",
    "    }",
    "}",
    "```",
    "",
    "shader的全局变量，直接使用Shader.SetGlobalFloat()方法进行赋值即可，对应的还有其它全局方法类型。",
    "",
    "",
    "",
    "",
    "",
    "## 局部修改",
    "",
    "<img class=\"blog-img blog-img-align-center\" src=\"assets/ImageWork/Blog/Shader/shader属性控制-02.png\" alt=\"图片\">",
    "",
    "",
    "```hlsl",
    "public class ChangeColorPerRenderer : MonoBehaviour",
    "{",
    "    ",
    "    public Color newColor = Color.green;",
    "    private Renderer _renderer;",
    "    private MaterialPropertyBlock _propBlock;",
    "",
    "    void Start()",
    "    {",
    "        _propBlock = new MaterialPropertyBlock();",
    "        _renderer = GetComponent<Renderer>();",
    "    }",
    "",
    "    void Update()",
    "    {",
    "        Color crrrentColor = _propBlock.GetColor(\"_GlobalColor\");",
    "        float lerpedValue = Mathf.Lerp(0.0f, 1.0f, Mathf.PingPong(Time.time * 0.05f, 1.0f));",
    "        ",
    "        // 使用 MaterialPropertyBlock 修改颜色（不影响其他使用相同材质的对象）",
    "        _renderer.GetPropertyBlock(_propBlock);",
    "        _propBlock.SetColor(\"_GlobalColor\", Color.Lerp(crrrentColor , newColor , lerpedValue)); // \"_Color\" 是在 Shader 中定义的变量",
    "        _renderer.SetPropertyBlock(_propBlock);",
    "        ",
    "        //如果使用该方法，会全局进行修改",
    "        // Shader.SetGlobalColor(\"_GlobalColor\", Color.Lerp(Color.green,Color.red,Mathf.PingPong(Time.time*0.5f , 1.0f)));",
    "    }",
    "}",
    "```"
  ]
}